{"tid":1937893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO好撚有用，特區護照無能","createTime":"2020-03-22T07:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T10:37:31.000Z","uid":269629,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8fc6b62e52a2323f175aed6fe9edd2937eca856","tid":1937893,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:56:40.000Z","msg":"一招ko感恩撚。<br />\n<br />\n包機要俾錢又點，起碼英國領事館做到野，等你走得到。唔使坐架靈車旅遊巴，唔係感謝中共。<br />\n<br />\n英鎊歷史新低，有BNO而未續期快的搞。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，唔需要批評陳先生兩夫婦。指向正確目標，拉攏支持，就係睇清特區護照無用，英國政府絕非佛系。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n/他說，曾經向中國和香港政府求助，但得不到積極回應。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「我們一知道鎖國時，已經問過（香港）入境處，但處方告訴我沒有摩洛哥封城的消息，然後叫我們求助中國使領館，但大使館方面只弄了一個微信公眾號叫我們關注，從頭到尾，都沒有立案登記我們的資料。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n後來，身在香港的立法會議員收到香港人求助後公開事件，入境處表示，接獲百多宗求助個案，將積極跟進和協助當地港人離開。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>他在當地認識了持英國國民海外（BNO）護照的港人，BNO是香港主權移交前英國向港人批出沒有居留權的護照。這些BNO持有人曾經向英國使領館求助，他們提早接獲英國政府通知，得悉英國方面安排了新增的特殊航班，可以讓他們離開。</strong><br />\n<br />\n英國政府和摩洛哥政府協調後，特別加開了100班飛機接走遊客。這些特殊航班在運作上，並不限於只接走英國國民，而是航空公司獲准加開航班後，循正常途徑售出機票，其他國籍的人都可以申請。<br />\n<br />\n如果不是BNO持有人提前從英國外交部職員得知消息，機票可能早被搶光。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生和太太在17日凌晨12時許，睡夢中被其他港人弄醒獲告知相關消息，及時買到這張當天下午約1時前往英國的機票。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「我體會到，你在海外遇難時，香港和中國政府不一定幫得上忙，」他說。</strong><br />\n<br />\n「在網上見到批評，我都有點介意，我們不是想花公帑，只是想政府發聲，特許一些航班讓我們離開，<strong>我們當時是有錢也買不到離開的機會，不是想政府免費包機，只要做到英國這樣就足夠。</strong>」/<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51971751?SThisFB&amp;fbclid=IwAR1clCalsethANRCXMa3fohzBYBqHNIFn-JAwF-0pGiQn_nJNs2N2ktBY20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51971751%3FSThisFB%26fbclid%3DIwAR1clCalsethANRCXMa3fohzBYBqHNIFn-JAwF-0pGiQn_nJNs2N2ktBY20&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=ac3446b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51971751%3FSThisFB%26fbclid%3DIwAR1clCalsethANRCXMa3fohzBYBqHNIFn-JAwF-0pGiQn_nJNs2N2ktBY20&h=8c19d904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51971751?SThisFB&amp;fbclid=IwAR1clCalsethANRCXMa3fohzBYBqHNIFn-JAwF-0pGiQn_nJNs2N2ktBY20</a>"},{"pid":"97edda14ac569e8df41c3fefdec39956c0e3e7e3","tid":1937893,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推正面post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464df6fefb6549224cd035f306965eae4d3a075b","tid":1937893,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff6dfa76f92f920c701f7eb44fd6f05583dfdac","tid":1937893,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T08:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c4e333e54d0200a666d07acf2702e6b2bea131","tid":1937893,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6bdb8a9ba25a745b15e7f8627a4accb3b5a264","tid":1937893,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"929fc4a7663176619ae5d63fe840653a5aef9a3d","tid":1937893,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad49ddedc963a6ad547c31718bff06fe7654898a","tid":1937893,"uid":288641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:44:01.000Z","msg":"英國政府做野唔洗五毛式宣傳，低能做野就夠"},{"pid":"d47d2d642b6f2aee880f98196134d233c6cd4673","tid":1937893,"uid":269629,"like":0,"disli